mime\&.mimetypes\&.path \fB<str>\fR (default: "~/\&.mime\&.types:/etc/mime\&.types:/usr/etc/mime\&.types:/usr/local/etc/mime\&.types:/usr/share/mime\&.types:/usr/share/misc/mime\&.types")
.RS 4
The search path for
mime\&.types
files\&. Colon\-separated list of files\&.
.RE
