NNTP and news specific options\&.
.PP
protocol\&.nntp\&.server \fB<str>\fR (default: "")
.RS 4
Used when resolving news: URIs\&. If set to the empty string the value of the
\fBNNTPSERVER\fR
environment variable will be used\&.
